commit_message: Update README.md
Added the 'analysis' scripts that I have been using on local: chipPeakAnno.R, diffBind.R, overlapPeakVenn.R, runHomer.R. They haven't been tested on exacloud or on other data yet.
Updated README to have a brief introduction section describing how to use the pipeline. Updated helperFxns.R to have mkdir()
Update README to include a few dependencies that I hadn't caught before
Updated 10_run_bowtie2.sh to point to BIOCODERS so that you don't have to re-make index every time. Updated 02_trimViz.R to not need hardcoded treatment information.
Added homer code
Fixed file name substitution in bdg2bw step
Added all of the QC plotting scripts in qc/ and updated README with instructions

Merge branch 'master' of github.com:ohsu-cedar-comp-hub/ChIP-seq

Test
Update a few qc items and check formatting
Typo and formatting
Add need for Biocoders path to README
Added public tools to repo and updated scripts to match
Cleaned up all of the code - removed absolute paths, deleted old commented portions, etc.
Moved countPeaks to qc script directory. Added final bdgcmp and bw conversion for signal track output. Updated README extensively to include more information about output files and their uses.
Updated readme to contain information regarding peak calling portion

Re-named bowtie QC scripts. Removed dependency on bam files for filename from 10_bowtie_alignment_qc.R. This requires 10_run_bowtie2.sh to print the base file name to stderr along with the QC data that bowtie outputs automatically.
Moved processDupLog to QC as well
Move processTrimLog.sh to qc/ instead of in base code directory
Added support for skipping unzip step
Huge update. Forgot to commit for most of pipeline development. Pipeline is usable from file transfer to peak calling. QC scripts need final integration.
Updated bowtie2 path. Updated README. Updated setup.sh
Added readme
Updated bowtie summary scripts to use optParse. Also added numbers. Added more numbers to setup.sh directories.
Update log directories in setup. Update variables in filter and convert.
Update variables in sam to bam
Updated unzip to be simpler because fewer samples. Updated bowtie call to ignore the ref files in 00_fastqs. Also updated variable names.
Updated log location
Added reference to repo. Updated setup.sh to reflect.
First commit.
